caption:
What goes into harvesting the most nutrient-dense red meat in North America? This rare behind-the-scenes video gives you a glimpse into an amazing operation. You can find the full-length 5-minute version on Momentous’s YouTube channel.

Great collab between @mauinuivenison and @live.momentous. Long-term consumer and supporter of both. Fuel practically kept me alive for a week last fall in Colorado. I’d probably still be sleeping under a tarp up there without it. If you’re going hard and long, it really works.

To try their limited-edition POG Fuel, just go to tim.blog/pog Here’s what that does:

$10 of every Fuel purchase goes to Maui Nui’s Holo ’Ai food sharing program, which donates venison to food-insecure families on Maui. They’ve donated 800,000+ meals to date, and every meal makes a difference in the community.
